div.h1: Join Order Impact: Why Order Matters

div.p: The optimizer must estimate table sizes and choose the smaller table as the outer loop. With proper statistics (ANALYZE), it knows:

ul.li: Index exists on orders.customer_id Wrong order: O(N M) = O(10) operations Right order: O(K log M) = O(10 20) = O(210) operations

div.p: Outer loop: 1,000,000 iterations Inner lookups: 1M full scan Page reads: ~3,000,000 Time: ~30 seconds
Outer loop: 10,000 iterations Inner lookups: 10K index seek Page reads: ~50,000 Time: ~0.5 seconds
